</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="32A60017BD691E39BD610491AA6689C6" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" type="dimensions in mm">
<paragraph id="E2705B51D448969CBB7C4ECA3252B741" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Dimensions in mm</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F8ED27FB3D3CB90D545D1EC14FB66D32" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">(holotype male). Total length (from mandibular apex to abdominal apex), 11.80; prothorax: length, 2.70; anterior width, 1.65; posterior width, 1.70; humeral width, 2.30; elytral length, 7.70.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
